Package: discerner
Type: Package
Title: discerner: a method for differential analyses via hierarchical permutation tests
Version: 0.99.0
Author: Simone Tiberi [aut, cre], Mark D. Robinson [aut].
Maintainer: Simone Tiberi <simone.tiberi@uzh.ch>
Description: discerner is a general and flexible statistical method to perform, via hierarchical permutation tests, differential testing between two or more groups of distributions.
